00:39:18.540 --> 00:39:21.020
The magic formula
does beat the market.

00:39:21.020 --> 00:39:25.070
AUDIENCE: Yeah, but
I'm sure that he also

00:39:25.070 --> 00:39:30.660
has done the study on the
